  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandAliasHelpTopic  
    CustomHelpTopic
    This is a help topic implementation for general topics registered in the help.yml file.
    CustomIndexHelpTopic  
    HelpTopicAmendment
    A HelpTopicAmendment represents the contents of a topic amendment from the help.yml
    HelpYamlReader
    HelpYamlReader is responsible for processing the contents of the help.yml file.
    MultipleCommandAliasHelpTopic
    This is a help topic implementation for MultipleCommandAlias commands.
    MultipleCommandAliasHelpTopicFactory
    This class creates MultipleCommandAliasHelpTopic help topics from MultipleCommandAlias commands.
    SimpleHelpMap
    Standard implementation of HelpMap for CraftBukkit servers.
